<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div class="body"><iframe class="IsolatedDom-sc-h3zeen-0 kmHRJp"/><p class="reference" data-aid="154411232" id="reference1">&#x201C;July 29&#x2013;August 4: &#x2018;Look to God and Live.&#x2019; Alma 36&#x2013;38,&#x201D; <cite>Come, Follow Me&#x2014;For Home and Church: Book of Mormon 2024</cite> (2023)</p>
<p class="short-reference" data-aid="154411235" id="short_reference1">&#x201C;July 29&#x2013;August 4. Alma 36&#x2013;38,&#x201D; <cite>Come, Follow Me&#x2014;For Home and Church: 2024</cite> (2023)</p>
